<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Der Rat an Rüdel Spielfritz, Bürger zu Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat lädt Spielfritz unverzüglich vor.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_131" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_131_r1l11">Rüdel <expan>ſpılfrıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> genant <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l12">Rüdel ſpılfrıcʒ wır <expan>gebıete<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        dır bey dem eyd den du vns geſworn haſt daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l13">du <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>ʒogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> .
                        nach angeſıcht dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> ʒu vns herauf
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l15">des mıt nichte laſſen ſülleſt <add><ab facs="#facs_131_r1l14">daran tuſtu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab></add> . wan wır etlıch ſache mıt dır ʒu reden
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r1l16"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo
                                <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıcıuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> vt
                                <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_131" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Rüdel <expan>Spilfricze<ex>n</ex></expan> genant,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Rüdel Spilfricz, wir <expan>gebiete<ex>n</ex></expan> dir bey dem eyd, den
                        du uns gesworn hast, daz du <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>zogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        nach angesicht dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> zu uns herauf
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch des mit nichte lassen
                        süllest, <add>daran tus tu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, wan wir etlich sache mit dir zu
                        reden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri
                                civiu<ex>m</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
